README FILE

spiral.c: code to generate a json file with a scene with a double spiral made of spheres 
(one spiral is red, the other one is blue)

##### Compile ##### 
Compile using the math library (-lm)
gcc -Wall createSpiralScene.c -lm

##### Input: ######
Run with ./a.out > (output_file.json)
i.e.      ./a.out > myscene01.json

-origin and end of spiral in the xyz plane [x1, x2]
-position of the base [x, y, z]

i.e.       to draw an orizontal double spiral:
0 400   (from left to right side of picture)
0 200 100 (initial postion of spiral, on the left of the picture)
